-- Germany Lauds Peace Prize Winner Liu as `Brave Man,' Calls for His Release
-- B y   A l a n   C r a w f o r d
-- 2010-10-08T09:36:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-08/germany-lauds-peace-prize-winner-liu-as-brave-man-calls-for-his-release.html
The German government congratulated
Liu Xiaobo, a jailed Chinese dissident, on being awarded the
Nobel Peace Prize.  Liu is a “brave man” who should be freed, government
spokesman Steffen Seibert told reporters in Berlin today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
